snippet.title: RARE Japanese McDonald's Game (PC) Paso Pico McDonald's de Asobo! Video Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Paso Pico McDonald's de Asobo! (ぱそピコ マクドナルドであそぼ！), released as part of the Paso Pico series, is a PC remake of the Sega Pico game, McDonald's de Asobo!.

More McDonald's video games here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2lmBskBrV9au9KmzebLR5JsJwbR1jity

McDonald's de Asobo!: https://youtu.be/Lqz3U43_toU
Hello Kitty to McDonald's de Asobo!: https://youtu.be/75f2sBhWvDo
